              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.These Measurements are not Possible by",
                "Standard Methods Because a Chemically Isolated Iodine",
                "Sample Contains About Ten Radioactive Isotopes with",
                "Half-Lives Ranging from 25 Min to 60 Days.In the Search",
                "For a Technique Capable of Differentiating Between",
                "These Isotopes the Possibility of Using Electromagnetic",
                "Separation After the Chemical Procedure was Considered."
